body: I’ve been thinking “I wish thirteen wasn’t so expositional” but I was just thinking through trying to see if anyone else has been and honestly the tenth doctor was super expositional too. He stopped to explain everything all the time; and he was hella patronizing about it. Thirteen has been just very matter of fact and occasionally angry or worried in explaining things
